- **T022**: T021\n142: - **T030**: None (new file creation)\n143: - **T031**: T030\n144: - **T032**: T031\n145: - **T033**: T032\n146: - **T040**: All implementation tasks (T001-T033)\n147: - **T041**: T040\n148: - **T042**: T041\n149: - **T043**: T041\n150: \n151: ---\n152: \n153: ## Configuration Variables\n154: \n155: ### agentd\n156: \n157: | Variable | Required | Default | Description |\n158: |----------|----------|---------|-------------|\n159: | KUBECONFIG | No | in-cluster | Kubernetes config path |\n160: \n161: ### picod\n162: \n163: | Variable | Required | Default | Description |\n164: |----------|----------|---------|-------------|\n165: | KUBECONFIG | No | in-cluster | Kubernetes config path |\n166: \n167: ### workload-manager\n168: \n169: | Variable | Required | Default | Description |\n170: |----------|----------|---------|-------------|\n171: | --listen-address | No | :8080 | HTTP server listen address |\n172: | --kubeconfig | No | in-cluster | Kubernetes config path |\n173: | --shutdown-timeout | No | 30s | Graceful shutdown timeout |\n174: \n175: ### router\n176: \n177: | Variable | Required | Default | Description |\n178: |----------|----------|---------|-------------|\n179: | --listen-address | No | :8080 | HTTP server listen address |\n180: | --workload-manager-url | Yes | - | WorkloadManager backend URL |\n181: \n182: ---\n183: \n184: ## Architecture Notes\n185: \n186: ### Binary Entry Points\n187: \n188: | Binary | Entry Point | Purpose |\n189: |--------|-------------|---------|\n190: | agentd | cmd/agentd/main.go | Kubernetes controller for AgentRuntime/CodeInterpreter CRDs |\n191: | picod | cmd/picod/main.go | Code execution daemon inside sandbox pods |\n192: | router | cmd/router/main.go | HTTP session router with auth/session management |\n193: | workload-manager | cmd/workload-manager/main.go | REST API for sandbox lifecycle management |\n194: \n195: ### Key Behaviors\n196: \n197: 1. **agentd**: Runs as K8s controller using controller-runtime, watches Sandbox resources\n198: 2. **picod**: HTTP server for code execution inside sandbox pods\n199: 3. **router**: Proxies requests to workload-manager, handles session affinity\n200: 4. **workload-manager**: REST API that creates/manages AgentRuntime CRs\n201: \n202: ### Package Dependencies\n203: \n204: - `cmd/agentd` → `pkg/agentd`\n205: - `cmd/picod` → `pkg/picod`\n206: - `cmd/router` → `pkg/router`, `pkg/store`\n207: - `cmd/workload-manager` → `pkg/workloadmanager`, `pkg/client`\n208: \n209: ---\n210: \n211: ## References\n212: \n213: - Design Doc: `design.md` (AR-019)\n214: - Module: `cmd`\n215: - Related: `pkg/agentd`, `pkg/picod`, `pkg/router`, `pkg/workloadmanager`\n\n(End of file - total 215 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-019 — CLI Binary Entry Points (4 Binaries) Tasks\n\n**Module:** cmd  \n**Language:** Go  \n**Size:** M  \n**Stage:** ST-3 (Design Complete)\n\n---\n\n## Implementation Tasks\n\n### Phase 1: Verify/Complete agentd (cmd/agentd/main.go)\n\n- [ ] **T001** Verify `cmd/agentd/main.go` - confirm it compiles and matches design:\n  - Uses controller-runtime manager\n  - Watches Sandbox CRD\n  - Imports `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/agentd` reconciler\n  - Metrics disabled (`BindAddress: \"0\"`)\n  - Health probe disabled\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-019/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775859826929,"end":1775859826943}}}}
